thread.title: TV | The Sin Bin

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | The Sin Bin
text: Final episode of this new TV3 sports comedy show tonight, which has seen presenters Joe Molloy and Andrew Maxwell talk all things Rugby World Cup with some special guests along the way. Joining them tonight will be Ulster and Ireland rugby star Stephen Ferris, former Wallabies captain Rocky Elsom, and last but not least, Belfast comedian Colin Murphy.
